{"tid":765917,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本取代中國 成為全球第二大股市","createTime":"2018-08-03T07:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T03:36:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"deadac81ca7e11e8dc63df73bf7cf18d898832ea","tid":765917,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T07:22:16.000Z","msg":"貿易戰陰霾下，A股今年跌跌不休，中國內地被日本所取代，不再是繼美國後第二大股市。據彭博統計，截至昨日收市，內地滬深股市市值降至6.09萬億美元（47.5萬億港元），低於日股的6.17萬億美元，美國繼續擁全球最大股市，市值31萬億美元，遠遠拋離日本。<br />\n<br />\nA股於2014年取代日本成為全球最大股市，2015年曾創10萬億美元的歷史高位，但上證綜指今年累挫逾16%，為全球最差股市之一，人民幣兌美元亦累挫5.3%；日股主要股指Topix今年累跌3.9%，為亞股中表現較好市場，主要受惠日本央行持續購買ETF及企業盈利帶動。<br />\n<br />\n有關市值的計算只計及第一上市，內地股市市值亦未計及港股的5.1萬億美元，若計及中港三地交易所，大中華三地股市市值則超過日股。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://invest.hket.com/article/2129492/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%20%20%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%A4%A7%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finvest.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2129492%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%258F%2596%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2520%2520%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2582%25A1%25E5%25B8%2582&d=ubKrzgiQmVzJPhp33jvs0hxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=4ce2fe6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://invest.hket.com/article/2129492/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%20%20%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%A4%A7%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82</a>"},{"pid":"b053c430413949400a23b814e992fedfb06f4bc6","tid":765917,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T07:32:43.000Z","msg":"香港去佐邊？"},{"pid":"348776430ccae70eb774018df6d2726e602f3038","tid":765917,"uid":179938,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:04:56.000Z","msg":"大你老母中華咩，三地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95607da51fb0a362840bd58d39bff4ae4b128608","tid":7